      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;SIRUI 50mm f1.8 Anamorphic cine cinema obiettivo obiettivi lens lenti lente 1.33x  E Mount  APS-C&lt;/a&gt; qui:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41stShU8g5L._SL500_._SL400_.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;SIRUI 50mm f1.8 Anamorphic cine cinema obiettivo obiettivi lens lenti lente 1.33x  E Mount  APS-C&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ℹ️:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Il primo obiettivo anamorfo a prezzi accessibili per tutti. Per film widescreen in formato cinema 2.4:1&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Design robusto ma leggero in lega di alluminio aeronautico di alta qualità e elementi in vetro Schott prodotti in Germania&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Crea effetti cineastici come riflessi Sci-Fi orizzontali, effetti di luce impressionanti e un bokeh ovale&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Attacco obiettivo: E-Mount (ad esempio per Sony NEX e Alpha). Campo visivo più ampio del 33% rispetto agli obiettivi tradizionali da 50 mm. Equivalente a circa un campo visivo di 37,5 mm&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Lunghezza focale: 50 mm (equivalente a 75 mm) | Diaframma: f/1. 8 - F/16. Distanza ravvicinata: 0. 85 m fino allinfinito. Messa a fuoco: manuale. Copertura del sensore: fino allAPS-C.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🛒 Acquista qui!!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA;   Check the price of this item in other countries:&lt;p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees0a-21&#34;&gt;🇬🇧 United Kingdom&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees-20&#34;&gt;🇺🇸 USA&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;🇩🇪 Germany&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.es/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees-21&#34;&gt;🇪🇸 Spain&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.fr/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees0d-21&#34;&gt;🇫🇷 France&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🇮🇹 Italia&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.ae/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=rdkn01-21&#34;&gt;🇦🇪 Arab Emirates&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.ca/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=rdkn0d-20&#34;&gt;🇨🇦 Canada&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com.be/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=rdkn0c-21&#34;&gt;🇧🇪 Belgium&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.nl/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=lgtm05-21&#34;&gt;🇳🇱 Neederlands&lt;/a&gt; |      &#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.pl/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=rdkn073-21&#34;&gt;🇵🇱 Poland&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.se/dp/B07KD1P5ZY/?tag=rdkn0a-21&#34;&gt;🇸🇪 Sweden&lt;/a &gt; |&#xA;   &lt;/p&gt;</description>
